'''甲状腺功能亢进症'''（Hyperthyroidism），又稱'''甲狀腺機能亢進症'''，簡稱'''甲狀腺亢進'''、'''甲亢'''，是一种由于体内过量的[[三碘甲腺原氨酸|三碘甲腺原氨酸]]（T3）和 [[四碘甲腺原氨酸|四碘甲腺原氨酸]]（T4，也即甲状腺素）造成的[[临床症状|临床症状]]。而甲狀腺毒症（Thyrotoxicosis）是因為任何原因，甲狀腺激素過多所造成的症狀，當然也包括甲狀腺機能亢進症<ref name="ATA2011">{{Cite journal|title=Hyperthyroidism and other causes of thyrotoxicosis: management guidelines of the American Thyroid Association and American Association of Clinical Endocrinologists|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/21510801|last=Bahn Chair|first=Rebecca S.|last2=Burch|first2=Henry B.|date=2011-06|journal=Thyroid: Official Journal of the American Thyroid Association|issue=6|doi=10.1089/thy.2010.0417|volume=21|pages=593–646|issn=1557-9077|pmid=21510801|last3=Cooper|first3=David S.|last4=Garber|first4=Jeffrey R.|last5=Greenlee|first5=M. Carol|last6=Klein|first6=Irwin|last7=Laurberg|first7=Peter|last8=McDougall|first8=I. Ross|last9=Montori|first9=Victor M.|access-date=2021-09-25|archive-date=2022-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220114090012/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/21510801/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。不過有時這二個詞語也會混用<ref>{{cite web|title=Hyperthyroidism, Thyroid Storm, and Graves Disease|url=http://emedicine.medscape.com/article/767130-overview|accessdate=20 April 2015|author=Erik D Schraga|date=May 30, 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150405111836/http://emedicine.medscape.com/article/767130-overview|archive-date=2015-04-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。其症狀及體徵因人而異，可能包括煩躁、肌肉無力、無法入睡、[[心跳过速|心跳过速]]、{{le|畏热|Heat intolerance}}、[[腹瀉|腹瀉]]、[[甲状腺肿|甲状腺肿]]以及體重減輕。年紀較大或是懷孕中的婦女症狀較不典型<ref name="NIH2012">{{Cite web|title=Hyperthyroidism|url=http://www.niddk.nih.gov/health-information/health-topics/endocrine/hyperthyroidism/Pages/fact-sheet.aspx|accessdate=2015-04-02|date=July 2012|website=www.niddk.nih.gov|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150404183926/http://www.niddk.nih.gov/health-information/health-topics/endocrine/hyperthyroidism/Pages/fact-sheet.aspx|archive-date=2015-04-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

有一種少見的併發症稱為[[甲狀腺風暴|甲狀腺風暴]]，其中也會因為感染使病情惡化，會有意識不清、發高燒等症狀，甚至會導致死亡<ref name=Clin2014/>。[[甲狀腺機能低下症|甲狀腺機能低下症]]是和甲狀腺機能亢進症相反的疾病，是指甲狀腺無法分泌足夠的甲狀腺激素<ref>{{cite web|title=Hypothyroidism|url=http://www.niddk.nih.gov/health-information/health-topics/endocrine/hypothyroidism/Pages/fact-sheet.aspx|accessdate=20 April 2015|author=NIDDK|date=March 13, 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305010654/http://www.niddk.nih.gov/health-information/health-topics/endocrine/hypothyroidism/Pages/fact-sheet.aspx|archive-date=2016-03-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

甲状腺激素水平正常，而TSH水平下降者，应考虑'''亚临床甲亢'''<ref>{{Cite web|title=Hyperthyroidism(Thyrotoxicosis)|url=http://www.merckmanuals.com/professional/endocrine_and_metabolic_disorders/thyroid_disorders/hyperthyroidism.html|accessdate=2011-11-25|author=Jerome M. Hershman|publisher=Merck & Co., Inc.|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111124014359/http://www.merckmanuals.com/professional/endocrine_and_metabolic_disorders/thyroid_disorders/hyperthyroidism.html|archive-date=2011-11-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。亚临床甲亢患者“可以”出现甲状腺毒症的临床表现<ref>{{Cite web|title=Hyperthyroidism and other causes of thyrotoxicosis：management guidelines of the American Thyroid Association and American Association of Clinical Endocrinologists|url=http://thyroidguidelines.net/sites/thyroidguidelines.net/files/file/THY_2010_0417.pdf|accessdate=2011-12-04|author=Rebecca S. Bahn et al|publisher=the American Thyroid Association and American Association of Clinical Endocrinologists|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120915230104/http://thyroidguidelines.net/sites/thyroidguidelines.net/files/file/THY_2010_0417.pdf|archivedate=2012-09-15|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。（而一般“亚临床”一词指的是疾病很轻微，尚没有临床表现）。

== 病因 ==
美國甲狀腺亢進的病例中，約有50%至80%是因為[[弥漫性毒性甲状腺肿|弥漫性毒性甲状腺肿]]而造成<ref name="NIH2012" /><ref name="NEJM2008">{{Cite journal|title=Graves' Disease|url=http://www.nejm.org/doi/abs/10.1056/NEJMcp0801880|last=Brent|first=Gregory A.|date=2008-06-12|journal=New England Journal of Medicine|issue=24|doi=10.1056/NEJMcp0801880|volume=358|pages=2594–2605|language=en|issn=0028-4793|pmid=18550875}}</ref>。其他的病因包括多結節性[[甲状腺肿|甲狀腺腫]]、[[甲狀腺腫瘤|甲狀腺腺瘤]]、[[甲狀腺炎|甲狀腺炎]]、[[碘|碘]]食用過量，以及過量的合成[[甲狀腺激素|甲狀腺激素]]<ref name="NIH2012" /><ref name=Clin2014>{{Cite journal|title=Hyperthyroidism and thyrotoxicosis|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/24766932|last=Devereaux|first=Danielle|last2=Tewelde|first2=Semhar Z.|date=2014-05|journal=Emergency Medicine Clinics of North America|issue=2|doi=10.1016/j.emc.2013.12.001|volume=32|pages=277–292|issn=1558-0539|pmid=24766932|access-date=2021-09-25|archive-date=2022-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220114082438/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/24766932/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。也有可能是因為{{tsl|en|Pituitary adenoma|垂體腺瘤}}導致，但這比較少見。
